title: Wendi Deng visits Ivanka Trump at her Washington DC home
text: EXCLUSIVE: Guess who's coming to dinner? Wendi Deng makes surprise trip to visit best friend Ivanka Trump in Washington DC and enjoys Shabbat dinner with her and Jared Kushner Wendi Deng traveled down to Washington DC on Friday afternoon to visit her friend Ivanka Trump Rupert Murdoch's 48-year-old ex-wife had not seen Ivanka, 35, since the inauguration over a month ago It was the perfect weekend for Wendi to get away as daughters Chloe and Gracie were in Europe and boyfriend Bertold Zahoran was working in Spain Deng did not depart the home before sundown, suggesting that she would be staying for Shabbat dinner Iavnka and husband Jared Kushner were part of the select group invited to Jordan in 2010 for Chloe and Grace's baptism in the River Jordan Published: 00:26 GMT, 25 February 2017 | Updated: 02:24 GMT, 25 February 2017 149 shares
